  "body": "In general, we can experience multiple issues if a hosting machine is slow (disk, network etc). \r\nFor example the node will struggle to sync with the network. Usually, we can use Grafana to read the metrics or read the logs.\r\nIt would be good to warn users if for example disk reads/writes are very slow or network communication is below expectations.",
